<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>MYANCHOR HOLDS</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka thagau tui kinawk leh,
 Huihpi lakah um mahleh;
 Ka lungmuong hi zehi hen,
 Huihpi hat hungnung mahleh;
 Tikchan ale muonum zing,
 Bitna thikdet ka nei hi.

[V2]
 Ka thikdet chun a tu det,
 Ka kuong neu leh dengdel chuh;
 Huihpi, hattawp in mutin,
 A hehpih vang puk puong ka,
 Ka thikdet chun a tukdet ziekin.

[V3]
 2. Tui kinawk in ei um ui,
 Tui nuoiah lauhum a um;
 Van nim in khawvak a lieh,
 Huihpi, guohpi a hungtung;
 Mahleh bittak in a ka ding,
 Thikdet suongpi-a kinga'n.

[V4]
 3. Thikdet muonum zie ka hei,
 Lauhum hungtun zing laiin;
 Muhloh ginna thikkhau in,
 Pathien tawh ka kiho zing;
 Tuikinawk lauhum lakah,
 Bittak in ka chieh pai hi.

[V5]
 4. Ka thagau buoinan a tuom,
 Lungkhamna tuibanga lien;
 Thepna'n puihmang di'n ei zawl,
 Thepna meipi'n ni a lieh;
 Krista ziekin hangsan ka,
 Thikdet muonum ka nei hi.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>323</hymn_number>
</song>